<h5>Secure and compliant by design</h5></div><p>By encrypting PII at the edge, it’s easier than ever to make your software secure and compliant by design.</p></div><div><div class="Features_featureTitle__oyjT_"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-construction"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="8" rx="1"></rect><path d="M17 14v7"></path><path d="M7 14v7"></path><path d="M17 3v3"></path><path d="M7 3v3"></path><path d="M10 14 2.3 6.3"></path><path d="m14 6 7.7 7.7"></path><path d="m8 6 8 8"></path></svg><h5>Eliminate the risk of a data breach</h5></div><p>Using evervault, all sensitive PII is encrypted in your database and at runtime — so even if you get breached, there’s no risk of sensitive data going missing.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="Testimonials_container__6YNup"><div class="Testimonials_maxWidthWrapper__qThI_"><div class="Testimonials_logosContainer__89AxU"><img src="../_next/static/media/logo-wheel.e71e91f2.svg" class="Testimonials_logosWheel__UhyCV" style="transform:none"/></div><h3 class="Testimonials_quote__HOJXC" id="swan-quote" style="opacity:0"><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">Q</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">L</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">L</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">H</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">P</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar"> </span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">X</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">+</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">P</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">Q</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar"> </span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">u</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar">h</span><span class="Testimonials_character__XOkar"> </span><span 